name: ReviveEth
additional_notices: Kindly be aware of liquidity-related risks. This notice is not directed at any project in particular, and is more of a cautionary reminder.

description.en: $Revive is an innovative token designed to revive your crypto bags and foster a thriving community $Revive places great emphasis on community engagement and participation. Regular community events, such as AMAs , live discussions, and voting mechanisms, foster an inclusive environment where members can actively contribute to the project's development. This collaborative approach ensures that the $Revive community plays an integral role in shaping the token's future.
